snippet.title: Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Siege – Crystal Guard Reveal Panel
snippet.description:
Crystal Guard is clearing its way right to our Rainbow Six Siege's battlefield. 3 map reworks, a new Elite skin customisation feature and many more tweaks are coming to Crystal Guard alongside Osa, Team Rainbow's new operator. 
Learn more: https://rainbow6.com/crystalguard
